data.description: Come tour this well-kept gem inside city limits! At 1.7 acres you'll have plenty of room for activities without having to break the bank. Highlights of this property include: A fully fenced yard with security gate access, mature trees that shade the house keeping your utility bills low, oversized bedrooms, a large laundry/mud room, plenty of storage, a super-efficient wood stove and a very convenient location within walking distance of all the amenities Cave Junction has to offer! This is a wonderful property to raise a family in. Schedule a showing today!
